Title.English: FIFA World Cup 2026 Asian Arabic Teams in World Cup 2026
Title.Arabic: FIFA World Cup 2026 Asian Arabic Teams in World Cup 2026

Remarks.English: Three Arabic teams from Asia qualified to the 2026 World Cup. Jordan for the first time in its history, Qatar for the first time through the qualifiers after its first participation as a host country for the 2022 World Cup, and Saudi Arabia, which qualified for the seventh time through the qualifiers and will host the 2034 World Cup.
